  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc3\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0daf\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0db8\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The United States of America is in a severe inflationary crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After US inflation hit a 40-year high, the Fed is expected to raise interest rates again this month by 100 basis points.",
        "Data from the Labor Department showed that rising gas, food and rental prices led to a 9.1% increase in the consumer price index (CPI) last month from a year earlier.",
        "While there are expectations that the Fed will be more aggressive in curbing inflation, there are also fears that it will disrupt the economy."
      ],
